OL,5,G2200 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,6,     FAn air ambulance is sent to help a
OL,7,     Ftree surgeon impaled on metal
OL,8,     Frailings; a 6-year-old is rushed
OL,9,     Fto hospital for head injuries; a
OL,10,     Fdouble amputee is found lying in a
OL,11,     Fpool of blood.
OL,12,G2300 Skin A&E
OL,13,     FFour top dermatologists treat
OL,14,     Fpatients for skin conditions such
OL,15,     Fas cysts, lipomas and skin tags
OL,16,     Fthat the NHS views as cosmetic,
OL,17,     Fbut that can hugely affect the
OL,18,     Fsufferers.
